'''Maryam Touzani''' (yavutse ku ya 18 Nyakanga 1980), niUmukinnyi wa firime muri Maroc  . <ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/maryam-touzani</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime yamamaye cyane ''Adam'' . <ref name="huffpostmaghreb">https://web.archive.org/web/20180317102056/http://www.huffpostmaghreb.com/2017/10/22/ils-font-le-cinema-mediterraneen-maryam-touzani-du-journalisme-au-cinema_n_18351198.html  </ref> <ref>https://variety.com/2019/film/festivals/filmmaker-maryam-touzani-talks-about-her-cannes-debut-adam-1203222994/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Touzani yavutse mu 1980 i Tangier . <ref>https://prixagnes.be/role-member/maryam-touzani/</ref> Mu 2003, yabonye impamyabumenyi ya Masters mu Itumanaho n'Itangazamakuru i Londres. Hanyuma yatangiye umwuga we nkumunyamakuru yibanda kuri sinema. <ref name="plurielle">https://www.plurielle.ma/lifestyle/arts-culture/le-film-choc-sur-aya-petite-bonne-marocaine/ </ref>

Yashakanye na mugenzi we bakorana amafilime n’igifaransa-Maroc Nabil Ayouch . <ref name="huffpostmaghreb">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://web.archive.org/web/20180317102056/http://www.huffpostmaghreb.com/2017/10/22/ils-font-le-cinema-mediterraneen-maryam-touzani-du-journalisme-au-cinema_n_18351198.html "They make Mediterranean cinema: Maryam Touzani, from journalism to cinema"]. huffpostmaghreb<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">3 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

== Umwuga ==
Ubwa mbere, yakoraga nk'umwanditsi w'amashusho hanyuma akayobora firime ngufi na documentaire. Muri 2011, yakoze ''Quand ils dorment'' . Yatsindiye ibihembo 17, harimo nk'abacamanza badasanzwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Huesca, iserukiramuco ryujuje ibisabwa na Oscars. <ref name="plurielle">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.plurielle.ma/lifestyle/arts-culture/le-film-choc-sur-aya-petite-bonne-marocaine/ "The shocking film about Aya, a little Moroccan maid"]. plurielle<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">3 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Hanyuma muri 2014, yakoze documentaire ye ya mbere ''Sous Ma Peau Vieille'' . Filime yamenyekanye cyane muri [[Maroke|Maroc]], yaganiriye ku buraya muri [[Maroke|Maroc]]. Intsinzi yiyi documentaire, yayihinduye muri firime yerekana izina ''Much Loved''  byasohotse muri 2015. Filime yayobowe numugabo we Nabil Ayouch mugihe yakoze inyandiko. <ref name="huffpostmaghreb">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://web.archive.org/web/20180317102056/http://www.huffpostmaghreb.com/2017/10/22/ils-font-le-cinema-mediterraneen-maryam-touzani-du-journalisme-au-cinema_n_18351198.html "They make Mediterranean cinema: Maryam Touzani, from journalism to cinema"]. huffpostmaghreb<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">3 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Mu mpera za 2015, yakoze ''plage ye ya kabiri Aya va à la plage'' . Filime irazenguruka mubindi bice byimibereho, kuriyi nshuro yerekeranye no gukoresha abana bato nkabakozi bo murugo. <ref>https://lematin.ma/express/2016/deux-court-metrages-marocains-en-competition-officielle/256128.html</ref>

Muri 2017, yanditse filime ''Razzia'' hamwe n'umugabo we, umuyobozi Nabil Ayouch. Yakinnye kandi 'Salima' muri filime. <ref>https://insidefarouche.com/2018/03/02/lactrice-et-realisatrice-maryam-touzani-a-les-femmes-dans-la-peau/</ref> Hanyuma, muri 2019, Touzani yayoboye filime ye yambere, ''Adam'' . <ref>https://vermelho.org.br/coluna/sem-direito-a-escolhas/</ref> Filime yatoranijwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes mu gice 'Un Certain Regard'. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20190419160301/https://www.huffpostmaghreb.com/entry/maryam-touzani-nous-parle-de-son-premier-long-metrage-adam-selectionne-au-festival-de-cannes-2019_mg_5cb9afc7e4b06605e3edac77</ref> Noneho nyuma muri Festival ya 12 International du Film Francophone de Namur ya Angoulême. Yatoranijwe nkuwinjiye muri Maroc muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga Mpuzamahanga mu bihembo bya 92 bya Academy, ariko ntiyatowe. <ref>http://french.xinhuanet.com/2019-08/28/c_138343359.htm</ref> <ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-2020-morocco-selects-adam-best-international-feature-category-1235102</ref>

Muri uwo mwaka, yabaye umunyamuryango wa Academy ya Oscars.  

